193. Telegram From the Department of State to the
                        Embassies in France and Vietnam
                    Source: National Archives and Records
                        Administration, RG 59, A/IM Files: Lot 93 D 82, HARVAN-(Outgoing)-November 1968. Secret;
                        Immediate; Nodis/HARVAN Double Plus. Drafted by Bundy; cleared by Rostow, Clifford, and Read;
                        and approved by Rusk.
